summary: I WAS TRAVELING NORTH OH HWY.45 OUT OF GALVESTON TX . THE CAR`S CRUSE CONTROL  WAS SET ON 60 MPH . I HAD JUST CLEARED THE LAST OVERPASS AND WAS ON THE FLAT ROAD WHEN THE MOTOR RAN UP TO 4000 RPM WITH NO SPEED INCREASE. THE CRUSE WAS STILL SET AT 60 MPH. . THE CAR BUMPED AND THE THE RPM. DROPPED TO 1600 RPM . I CALL THE DEALER AND THEY TOLD ME TO JUST DRIVE IT AND WATCH IT . I DON`T THINK THIS IS A NORMAL OPERATION .
